review_text: The stuff are very nice and helpful for everyone enter at the bank . I recommend to all people to open in this bank .

Great local bank with reasonable or no fees (ATM and checking or savings balance based) with friendly efficient tellers and good hours - open until 5 pm M-Th and closing at 6 pm on Friday + 1/2 day on Saturday.

They are so nice - the Manager even sent me a hand written Birthday Card. Nice touch! Recommended.

Tell me how it's okay for a bank to close at three in the afternoon during the week?! I'm very disappointed with this obvious lack of care for customers. It makes me ver upset that a person who work cannot get to his financial institution because they want to limit their hours.
